WEBVTT

00:02.000 --> 00:03.500
Previously on "Scandal"...

00:03.500 --> 00:05.250
Fitz: Make no mistake,
you are still a prisoner.

00:05.250 --> 00:06.620
Jake Ballard is no longer
an acceptable choice
for Vice President.

00:06.620 --> 00:08.920
We have
a very short list. Me.

00:08.920 --> 00:11.250
I am confident
you will handle the rest.

00:11.250 --> 00:12.880
What's going on?
A drone entered
White House airspace, sir --

00:12.880 --> 00:14.120
looks to be armed.

00:14.120 --> 00:15.580
Principals secure
in bunker five.

00:15.580 --> 00:17.460
Someone needs to tell me
what is happening.

00:17.460 --> 00:20.290
The drone is ours.
We're running a play in
order to take you back.

00:20.290 --> 00:22.830
I'm done losing.
I'm naming my own VP.

00:22.830 --> 00:24.040
I took Mellie back,

00:24.040 --> 00:25.960
and you are now
our prisoner.

00:25.960 --> 00:30.380
You can't take Olivia Pope.
Olivia Pope takes you.

00:30.380 --> 00:32.330
This has been
a very strange day.

00:32.330 --> 00:33.460
[ Chuckles ]

00:33.460 --> 00:35.750
I was certainly
not expecting the call

00:35.750 --> 00:37.960
I got from President-Elect Grant
this afternoon.

00:37.960 --> 00:39.580
And I must admit,

00:39.580 --> 00:41.670
my first impulse was
to say no to this appointment.

00:41.670 --> 00:43.790
But once I realized
it was real,

00:43.790 --> 00:46.790
something deep in my heart
told me

00:46.790 --> 00:48.540
this was meant to be.

00:48.540 --> 00:50.750
This was the opportunity

00:50.750 --> 00:54.170
to make my husband's death
mean something,

00:54.170 --> 00:58.080
to heal myself and this nation.

00:58.080 --> 00:59.920
What do we got?

00:59.920 --> 01:02.460
Woman: NORAD is tracking eight
bogies so far, Mr. President,

01:02.460 --> 01:04.120
each one over
a metropolitan area.

01:04.120 --> 01:05.210
They're up
on the screen.

01:05.210 --> 01:08.040
What are they?
High-end commercial drones

01:08.040 --> 01:09.500
modified to deliver
a payload, sir.

01:09.500 --> 01:11.580
Man: They're not registered
with the FAA,

01:11.580 --> 01:14.040
and they're being controlled
by an untraceable radio signal.

01:14.040 --> 01:15.500
The profile is similar
to the one

01:15.500 --> 01:17.210
that landed
on the south lawn today,

01:17.210 --> 01:18.290
but much scarier.

01:18.290 --> 01:20.080
The technology
has different markers,

01:20.080 --> 01:21.580
but it's the show of force
that concerns me --

01:21.580 --> 01:22.880
eight at once.

01:22.880 --> 01:25.620
Eight in this pattern --
it's a coordinated effort.

01:25.620 --> 01:27.380
[ Whispering ] There's a ninth
drone over Boston.

01:27.380 --> 01:28.710
Make that nine.

01:28.710 --> 01:32.040
A local news crew
just spotted one over Boston.

01:33.790 --> 01:36.420
Federal agents moved quickly
to evaluate a drone

01:36.420 --> 01:38.420
that has entered the airspace
over Boston.

01:38.420 --> 01:39.710
This makes nine drones

01:39.710 --> 01:41.580
currently hovering
over major U.S. cities,

01:41.580 --> 01:42.920
including Chicago and Dallas.

01:42.920 --> 01:44.120
Do you know
about this?

01:44.120 --> 01:46.170
Officials are trying
to determine

01:46.170 --> 01:47.790
who is responsible
for these unmanned aircraft...
[ Cellphone chimes ]

01:47.790 --> 01:50.500
...which resemble the drone
that landed on the south lawn

01:50.500 --> 01:51.960
of the White House
earlier today.
Olivia Pope.

01:51.960 --> 01:53.250
Peus: You have something
that belongs to me.

01:53.250 --> 01:54.540
Peus.

01:54.540 --> 01:55.830
Do you mean
your associate?

01:55.830 --> 01:57.460
I assure you,

01:57.460 --> 01:59.290
she's being given the same
respect you gave our loved ones.

01:59.290 --> 02:01.250
I mean Mellie Grant.
She's my President.

02:01.250 --> 02:02.670
I'm going to
need her back.

02:02.670 --> 02:03.670
Listen to me --

02:03.670 --> 02:05.170
No, you listen to me.

02:05.170 --> 02:08.120
You people may have been able
to protect your families,

02:08.120 --> 02:10.580
your loved ones,
as you call them,

02:10.580 --> 02:13.460
but in doing so, you put
the entire country at risk.

02:13.460 --> 02:18.080
Your little stunt today
with the drone -- inspiring.

02:18.080 --> 02:20.960
Who could have imagined
that one remote-controlled toy

02:20.960 --> 02:23.620
was capable
of generating so much fear.

02:23.620 --> 02:26.000
Imagine what nine
could accomplish.

02:26.000 --> 02:27.620
♪♪

02:27.620 --> 02:29.420
You're doing this.

02:29.420 --> 02:30.580
Correct.

02:30.580 --> 02:31.880
But unlike yours,

02:31.880 --> 02:33.830
mine are fully armed
and ready to blow.

02:33.830 --> 02:36.420
So, here's what's
going to happen next --

02:36.420 --> 02:38.250
I will
detonate the drones

02:38.250 --> 02:40.670
one by one
at random intervals

02:40.670 --> 02:42.420
until my President

02:42.420 --> 02:45.500
and yes, my associate, as well,
are released.

02:45.500 --> 02:49.000
Unless, of course,
you don't feel like gambling

02:49.000 --> 02:51.080
with the lives
of thousands of Americans

02:51.080 --> 02:53.210
and would rather
return them to me right now.

02:53.210 --> 02:54.830
You're pushing,
Peus.

02:54.830 --> 02:56.120
We both know no one,
not even you,

02:56.120 --> 02:57.460
has the resources to pull off
what you're describing

02:57.460 --> 02:58.620
in the amount of time --

02:58.620 --> 03:00.710
[ Explosion, static ]
[ Gasps ]

03:00.710 --> 03:02.290
♪♪

03:02.290 --> 03:03.710
[ Telephone ringing ]

03:03.710 --> 03:05.420
There's been an explosion
in Dallas, Mr. President.

03:05.420 --> 03:08.040
Man: Reports of casualties
are coming in.

03:09.670 --> 03:12.120
My God.

03:12.120 --> 03:13.620
Peus:
One down, Ms. Pope.

03:13.620 --> 03:16.120
Eight to go.

03:16.120 --> 03:19.290
I look forward
to hearing from you.

03:19.290 --> 03:21.040
[ Cellphone beeps ]

03:21.040 --> 03:23.830
♪♪

03:23.830 --> 03:25.830
[ Camera shutter clicking ]

03:30.120 --> 03:31.710
I want the National Guard
on the move.

03:31.710 --> 03:33.380
Coordinate with
local law enforcement

03:33.380 --> 03:35.460
on the immediate evacuation
of the affected city centers.

03:35.460 --> 03:37.120
And why isn't the
Director of FEMA on the phone?

03:37.120 --> 03:38.920
Someone get ahold of her, now!

03:38.920 --> 03:41.080
Where's my air analysis
over Dallas?

03:41.080 --> 03:43.500
Report's coming in now,
Mr. President.
Are the drones radioactive
or what?

03:43.500 --> 03:45.000
Unfortunately, we're not
able to make that
determination just yet.

03:45.000 --> 03:46.380
There's still
a very good chance

03:46.380 --> 03:48.210
there's more than a few
chemical agents on board.

03:48.210 --> 03:49.920
I need to know
what we're dealing with.

03:49.920 --> 03:51.830
I need answers, people --
definitive ones.

03:51.830 --> 03:53.920
Get some.

03:56.830 --> 03:59.170
Reporter: These horrific images
are coming out of Dallas,

03:59.170 --> 04:01.290
where a bomb exploded
mere minutes ago.

04:01.290 --> 04:03.750
First responders are just now
starting to arrive

04:03.750 --> 04:05.750
to assess the situation,
but as you can see,

04:05.750 --> 04:07.380
the blast hit several buildings

04:07.380 --> 04:10.170
and left many people injured,
possibly dead.

04:10.170 --> 04:11.460
Authorities are still trying

04:11.460 --> 04:13.120
to track down
the ones responsible --

04:13.120 --> 04:14.540
[ Television shuts off ]

04:14.540 --> 04:15.830
What are you doing?

04:15.830 --> 04:16.880
Drink with me.

04:18.080 --> 04:19.330
It's no DuBellay.

04:19.330 --> 04:20.790
We are not drinking.

04:20.790 --> 04:24.880
It's not even
a '94 Chateau D'yquem.

04:24.880 --> 04:27.170
Revolting,
their selection.

04:27.170 --> 04:28.250
We are at war.

04:28.250 --> 04:30.620
There is a war
happening out there.

04:30.620 --> 04:32.040
All the more reason

04:32.040 --> 04:33.880
to have one last drink
with your father,

04:33.880 --> 04:35.460
because that's
what this is, Olivia.

04:35.460 --> 04:36.920
[ Bottle thuds ]

04:36.920 --> 04:40.460
One last, final drink
before I go.

04:40.460 --> 04:42.620
You are not
going anywhere.

04:42.620 --> 04:44.250
Says who?
You?

04:44.250 --> 04:45.500
The President?

04:45.500 --> 04:46.710
[ Laughs ]
That's funny.

04:46.710 --> 04:47.830
So that's it?

04:47.830 --> 04:49.830
You just
want to run?

04:49.830 --> 04:52.620
When did you become a man
who runs away from anything?

04:52.620 --> 04:54.380
When I stopped
involving myself

04:54.380 --> 04:56.460
in affairs I have
absolutely nothing to do with.

04:56.460 --> 04:59.080
What about everything you built?
All that you've sacrificed?

04:59.080 --> 05:00.540
Everything that
you believe in?

05:00.540 --> 05:02.880
I made my peace
with those things long ago.

05:02.880 --> 05:04.040
What about me?

05:04.040 --> 05:06.210
You're free
to join me.
I'm not.

05:06.210 --> 05:07.880
I can't.
Why not?

05:07.880 --> 05:09.290
Because I'm not
done fighting.

05:09.290 --> 05:10.880
I haven't even begun
to make my peace.

05:10.880 --> 05:11.920
Not yet.

05:16.170 --> 05:17.420
Come upstairs with me.

05:17.420 --> 05:18.670
So I can die?

05:18.670 --> 05:20.080
Or worse,
watch you die?

05:20.080 --> 05:21.500
Dad --

05:21.500 --> 05:23.620
If you decide to stay here,
if you do not leave with me,

05:23.620 --> 05:25.040
that is
what will happen.

05:25.040 --> 05:28.290
You will die.

05:28.290 --> 05:31.040
♪♪

05:32.710 --> 05:35.000
I'll have them send down
some better wine for you, Dad.

05:35.000 --> 05:36.290
Hmm.

05:36.290 --> 05:38.710
[ Door opens ]

05:38.710 --> 05:39.830
[ Camera shutter clicking ]

05:39.830 --> 05:41.040
35 Americans dead,

05:41.040 --> 05:42.960
and that's just
as of three minutes ago.

05:42.960 --> 05:44.330
We need
to locate Peus.

05:44.330 --> 05:46.460
He's the one
who's controlling the drones.

05:46.460 --> 05:48.210
We find him,
all this ends.

05:48.210 --> 05:50.040
What if we tried tracing
the call that Peus made to Liv?

05:50.040 --> 05:51.460
Could we get his location
from his signal?

05:51.460 --> 05:52.880
Peus bounced it
off of satellites

05:52.880 --> 05:54.000
over Russia, Argentina,
Australia.

05:54.000 --> 05:55.460
I've got my boys in the NSA
working on it, but --

05:55.460 --> 05:58.080
Unfortunately, we don't exactly
have the luxury of time.

05:58.080 --> 05:59.710
Peus could detonate another bomb
at any second.

05:59.710 --> 06:02.580
These people --
they just want me.

06:02.580 --> 06:05.880
I say --
We don't negotiate
with terrorists, Mellie.

06:05.880 --> 06:07.710
Rosen, what's the name
of their front, that fake
super PAC they have?

06:07.710 --> 06:09.290
The Fund
for American Renewal.

06:09.290 --> 06:11.620
Fitz: I want you
to raid it -- now.

06:11.620 --> 06:13.210
We do still have an asset
in our custody --

06:13.210 --> 06:14.920
one who has the potential
to lead us

06:14.920 --> 06:16.210
straight to
Peus' doorstep.

06:19.790 --> 06:21.790
[ Door buzzes ]

06:23.790 --> 06:25.750
[ Door closes ]

06:25.750 --> 06:27.830
[ Door whirs ]
[ Sighs ]

06:30.500 --> 06:32.500
Where's Peus?

06:32.500 --> 06:34.920
Why?
Did something happen?

06:34.920 --> 06:36.620
Oh, Samantha.

06:36.620 --> 06:38.920
You...
are a ghost.

06:38.920 --> 06:40.580
Man after my own heart.

06:40.580 --> 06:42.380
Threats are
so much creepier

06:42.380 --> 06:43.790
when they come
with a smile.

06:43.790 --> 06:45.330
Oh, that wasn't
a threat.

06:45.330 --> 06:46.580
Just an observation.

06:46.580 --> 06:48.540
We've been trying
to figure out

06:48.540 --> 06:50.750
just who the hell you are
for weeks.

06:50.750 --> 06:52.710
You don't seem to have
anything resembling a life

06:52.710 --> 06:54.000
or a past.

06:54.000 --> 06:56.120
No high-school yearbook,
no prom photo,

06:56.120 --> 06:59.040
not even an I.D. badge from your
first job at the Dairy Queen.

06:59.040 --> 07:02.000
As far as the world knows,
you don't exist.

07:02.000 --> 07:04.580
I used to be
the same way.

07:04.580 --> 07:06.380
Twinsies.

07:06.380 --> 07:07.960
[ Chuckles ]

07:07.960 --> 07:10.120
I need to find Peus.

07:10.120 --> 07:12.290
I need you
to tell me where he is.

07:12.290 --> 07:13.540
You do that,

07:13.540 --> 07:15.380
I'll see to it
that you go free.

07:15.380 --> 07:19.120
You can hop on a boat,
sail out to some island...

07:19.120 --> 07:20.500
disappear.

07:20.500 --> 07:23.500
Well, that's just
not gonna happen, is it?

07:23.500 --> 07:24.710
Mm.
It's a legitimate offer.

07:24.710 --> 07:25.920
I doubt that.

07:25.920 --> 07:27.710
But even if it were,

07:27.710 --> 07:30.250
I'm not a person
who gets to disappear.

07:30.250 --> 07:32.580
Far too valuable
to my employer.

07:32.580 --> 07:34.620
He makes it his business
to know where I am

07:34.620 --> 07:36.790
every minute
of every hour of every day.

07:36.790 --> 07:38.750
The only way I disappear
is by a bullet.

07:38.750 --> 07:40.710
Either yours or his.

07:40.710 --> 07:43.000
And if
I were to trust you?

07:43.000 --> 07:45.080
If for some
unfathomable reason,

07:45.080 --> 07:46.540
I were to help you?

07:46.540 --> 07:49.960
He would track me all the way
to that little island paradise,

07:49.960 --> 07:51.120
and then he'd probably
just nuke the island.

07:52.790 --> 07:54.920
I kind of hoped
you might say that.

07:57.250 --> 07:59.500
[ Groans ]

07:59.500 --> 08:01.920
[ Grunting ]

08:01.920 --> 08:05.670
♪♪

08:12.040 --> 08:14.620
[ Breathing heavily ]

08:16.920 --> 08:19.040
I'll send someone in
with a Band-Aid.

08:19.040 --> 08:21.750
[ Chuckles ]

08:21.750 --> 08:24.620
[ Door beeps ]

08:29.830 --> 08:31.080
Did you get it?

08:31.080 --> 08:33.080
You really think you can
use this thing to find Peus?

08:33.080 --> 08:35.210
All I have to do is piggyback
onto the carrier signal

08:35.210 --> 08:37.620
and follow it all the way back
to its source location.

08:37.620 --> 08:39.040
Olivia:
That means yes.

08:39.040 --> 08:41.500
[ Camera shutter clicking ]
[ Beep ]

08:41.500 --> 08:42.880
The President has worked out

08:42.880 --> 08:44.380
a very thorough
disaster-relief plan.

08:44.380 --> 08:45.880
I just haven't had a chance

08:45.880 --> 08:47.420
to connect with him
on the specifics yet.

08:47.420 --> 08:48.670
After I speak with
the President,

08:48.670 --> 08:50.080
you'll be my first call,
Mayor Barta.

08:52.120 --> 08:55.460
[ Sighs ]

08:57.080 --> 08:58.290
[ Knock on door ]

08:59.460 --> 09:00.790
Red.

09:00.790 --> 09:02.790
Why are you here?
You mean in my office?

09:02.790 --> 09:04.670
Instead of in the Oval
with your boss,

09:04.670 --> 09:06.080
helping address
this national crisis.

09:06.080 --> 09:07.830
Well,
I've called four mayors.

09:07.830 --> 09:10.040
I have five more to go,
and then a conference call

09:10.040 --> 09:11.580
with the
House Armed Services Committee.

09:11.580 --> 09:13.380
He's frozen you out,
hasn't he?

09:13.380 --> 09:15.250
Did you need something,
Cyrus, or are you just
here to annoy me?

09:15.250 --> 09:16.670
Luna Vargas is asking
for a briefing.

09:16.670 --> 09:19.040
Press has been hounding her
since we announced her,

09:19.040 --> 09:21.040
and now with the drones,
I said she should talk to you.

09:21.040 --> 09:23.040
But that was when I thought
you actually knew something.

09:23.040 --> 09:24.420
I'd be happy to.

09:24.420 --> 09:25.500
Oh, Red, come on --
Get her in here!

09:25.500 --> 09:26.830
She's the
Vice President-Elect,

09:26.830 --> 09:28.960
and I'm
the President's Chief of Staff.

09:28.960 --> 09:30.500
[ Camera shutter clicking ]
[ Indistinct shouting ]

09:30.500 --> 09:32.540
The White House is speaking
with Mayor Silachi now

09:32.540 --> 09:33.960
to assess his needs,

09:33.960 --> 09:35.790
while the President
is actively working

09:35.790 --> 09:38.620
with the Joint Chiefs of Staff
to de-escalate the situation.

09:38.620 --> 09:40.000
[ Indistinct shouting ]
Here.

09:40.000 --> 09:42.040
Does that mean you know
who's behind the attacks?

09:42.040 --> 09:43.420
This is an ongoing threat.

09:43.420 --> 09:45.460
All tactical information
is classified.

09:45.460 --> 09:47.790
[ Indistinct shouting ]
Carol.

09:47.790 --> 09:49.830
So, you're saying you do know,
you just can't tell us?

09:49.830 --> 09:51.790
What I'm saying
is no comment.

09:51.790 --> 09:53.500
Are there any other questions?

09:53.500 --> 09:55.000
[ Indistinct shouting ]

09:55.000 --> 09:57.040
With only
two more weeks in office,

09:57.040 --> 09:59.120
is the President worried
that the string of attacks
will tarnish his legacy?

09:59.120 --> 10:00.620
The President is only concerned

10:00.620 --> 10:03.040
about the safety of the
American people at this time.

10:03.040 --> 10:04.960
[ Indistinct shouting ]

10:09.380 --> 10:11.420
Next question? Linda.

10:13.330 --> 10:14.420
How are we doing,
General?

10:14.420 --> 10:16.000
The UAVs
are being reprogrammed

10:16.000 --> 10:17.790
to function
in an urban environment.

10:17.790 --> 10:18.960
We're almost there,
Mr. President.

10:18.960 --> 10:20.670
Any chance of
knocking them out remotely?

10:20.670 --> 10:22.170
They're being controlled
by relay stations

10:22.170 --> 10:23.210
communicating with
a central hub.

10:23.210 --> 10:25.120
The only way
to stop them all

10:25.120 --> 10:26.500
would be to find
the central control location.

10:26.500 --> 10:28.210
Ballard's working
on that.

10:28.210 --> 10:29.790
Sir,
the drones are moving.

10:29.790 --> 10:30.790
[ Computer beeping ]

10:35.120 --> 10:36.540
I should have his location
in a couple of seconds.

10:37.960 --> 10:39.040
[ Computer beeping ]

10:40.500 --> 10:43.120
No, no, no!
What's happening?

10:43.120 --> 10:44.670
Something on the other end
triggered a kill switch

10:44.670 --> 10:45.460
in the
tracking chip's code.

10:45.460 --> 10:47.960
It's shutting me out.

10:47.960 --> 10:49.210
[ Sighs ]

10:49.210 --> 10:50.710
[ Cellphone ringing ]

10:50.710 --> 10:54.330
♪♪

10:55.960 --> 10:58.170
Mr. Peus.

10:58.170 --> 10:59.620
You're bothering me.
Am I?

10:59.620 --> 11:00.710
This is two --

11:00.710 --> 11:02.290
Two times
you've challenged me.

11:02.290 --> 11:03.830
Two insults.

11:03.830 --> 11:05.420
We are going to find you,
Mr. Peus, and when we do --

11:05.420 --> 11:06.920
I'm curious --
when's the last time

11:06.920 --> 11:08.830
you visited
the city of brotherly love?

11:08.830 --> 11:10.580
♪♪

11:11.880 --> 11:14.210
What are they doing?
They're taking
defensive positions,

11:14.210 --> 11:15.460
preparing for
an attack.

11:15.460 --> 11:16.790
I thought our Predators
weren't ready.

11:16.790 --> 11:18.750
Not our attack, sir.
Theirs.

11:18.750 --> 11:21.040
The Philadelphia drone's
heat signature is spiking.

11:21.040 --> 11:22.040
[ Computer beeping ]

11:22.040 --> 11:23.620
♪♪

11:23.620 --> 11:25.380
Just stop.
Please.

11:25.380 --> 11:27.540
My President-Elect
and my associate, Ms. Pope.

11:27.540 --> 11:28.540
I want them back.

11:28.540 --> 11:30.290
That's the only way
this stops.

11:30.290 --> 11:32.750
I don't have that authority.
I'm not the President.

11:32.750 --> 11:34.500
Aren't you?

11:34.500 --> 11:36.500
The United States
is not going to bend

11:36.500 --> 11:37.790
to the will
of a terrorist.

11:37.790 --> 11:39.670
That's a good line,
though I don't believe it.

11:39.670 --> 11:41.080
Mr. Peus --

11:41.080 --> 11:43.000
Talk soon, Ms. Pope.
Wait!

11:43.000 --> 11:44.330
[ Beeping continues ]

11:44.330 --> 11:46.290
[ Alarm blares ]

11:46.290 --> 11:47.500
Man: It's confirmed, sir.
No.

11:47.500 --> 11:49.120
The Philadelphia drone
detonated.

11:49.120 --> 11:51.250
[ Alarm continues ]

11:51.250 --> 11:54.710
♪♪

11:56.920 --> 11:57.960
[ Sighs ]

11:57.960 --> 12:00.210
Damn it!

12:00.210 --> 12:03.880
♪♪

12:08.460 --> 12:11.420
If you are just joining us,
we're following breaking news

12:11.420 --> 12:14.120
out of Philadelphia,
where an explosion was reported

12:14.120 --> 12:16.540
a few miles from
the 30th Street train station.

12:16.540 --> 12:18.380
While local emergency services

12:18.380 --> 12:20.620
are scrambling
to mitigate this disaster,

12:20.620 --> 12:22.880
all eyes turn
to the White House,

12:22.880 --> 12:25.830
hoping it can shed some light
on this dire situation.

12:25.830 --> 12:27.420
58 more casualties.

12:27.420 --> 12:29.620
58 more
American citizens dead

12:29.620 --> 12:31.540
because we can't find
one man.

12:31.540 --> 12:32.920
David Rosen
on Line One.

12:34.120 --> 12:35.330
[ Door closes ]

12:35.330 --> 12:37.040
Tell me
you found Peus.

12:37.040 --> 12:38.920
David: He's not in his home
or his office.

12:38.920 --> 12:40.620
We seized his computers.
Bunch of files.

12:40.620 --> 12:41.620
Talked to his staff.

12:41.620 --> 12:43.040
No indication
of where he is

12:43.040 --> 12:44.920
or how
he's operating the drones.

12:44.920 --> 12:46.120
Okay,
keep me posted.

12:47.580 --> 12:50.120
Are we
this incompetent?

12:50.120 --> 12:52.380
It looks bleak
right now --

12:52.380 --> 12:53.710
Your father
needs to start talking.

12:53.710 --> 12:55.250
He's not going to.

12:55.250 --> 12:57.330
He just wants to run.

12:57.330 --> 12:58.500
That's unacceptable.
We are at war.

12:58.500 --> 13:00.880
Fitz, those people
controlled him.

13:00.880 --> 13:02.000
Beat him.

13:02.000 --> 13:03.540
He may not even
know anything.

13:03.540 --> 13:06.500
You believe that Rowan,
master manipulator,

13:06.500 --> 13:08.670
spent six months
captive with these people

13:08.670 --> 13:10.540
and didn't cull
anything useful?

13:10.540 --> 13:12.670
Anything that could end
this carnage?

13:12.670 --> 13:15.000
Anything that could help
save this nation

13:15.000 --> 13:16.670
in the final weeks
of my Presidency?

13:21.750 --> 13:23.920
Let's go.

13:27.120 --> 13:29.580
I have
no help to give,

13:29.580 --> 13:31.000
nor a desire
to give it.

13:31.000 --> 13:34.000
The only desire I have
is to leave, run --

13:34.000 --> 13:35.420
with my daughter.

13:35.420 --> 13:37.380
Change your mind yet,
Olivia?

13:37.380 --> 13:40.080
I'm staying,
Dad.
Because she's a patriot.

13:40.080 --> 13:42.330
Is that meant to mean
that I am not?!
Americans are dying!

13:42.330 --> 13:43.750
Our country
is under attack.

13:43.750 --> 13:45.460
And because
you've finally decided

13:45.460 --> 13:47.040
to pick your head up
from the sandbox

13:47.040 --> 13:50.330
only to notice that the Republic
is crumbling under your watch,

13:50.330 --> 13:52.420
I'm the one who's
supposed to wipe your chin

13:52.420 --> 13:53.960
and clean
your bottom

13:53.960 --> 13:55.920
and make you look like
the leader of the free world?!

13:55.920 --> 13:57.460
Dad!

13:57.460 --> 13:58.960
As far as I am concerned,
you're one of them.

13:58.960 --> 14:01.250
[ Laughs ]
You assassinated
Frankie Vargas.

14:01.250 --> 14:03.250
The only reason
you're not frying right now

14:03.250 --> 14:04.710
is because
you can help.

14:04.710 --> 14:06.960
Your threats to me
do not change reality.

14:06.960 --> 14:08.210
Game over.

14:08.210 --> 14:09.420
They win.
You lose.

14:09.420 --> 14:12.620
We need to find Peus.
Step these bombs.

14:12.620 --> 14:13.790
Right.

14:13.790 --> 14:15.830
You want me
to pull you from the quicksand

14:15.830 --> 14:18.710
so that you can immediately
tumble off the cliff?

14:18.710 --> 14:20.080
You were working
with them!

14:20.080 --> 14:22.080
Let go!!
This?

14:22.080 --> 14:24.080
It's part of their plan,
isn't it?

14:24.080 --> 14:26.210
Fitz, let go.
Tell your boyfriend
he is three seconds away

14:26.210 --> 14:27.670
from having both of his arms
snapped in half!

14:27.670 --> 14:29.120
Fitz!

14:32.250 --> 14:37.000
The only thing that explains why
you're sitting on the sidelines

14:37.000 --> 14:39.250
while the Republic is
under attack is that
you're working with them.

14:39.250 --> 14:42.580
What about protecting
the Republic?

14:42.580 --> 14:46.080
Sacrificing for
the Republic?

14:46.080 --> 14:48.420
How many patriots
have you murdered in
the name of the Republic?

14:48.420 --> 14:50.790
There is
no Republic!!

14:50.790 --> 14:52.540
Look around!

14:52.540 --> 14:54.710
The Republic?!
Is in ashes.

14:54.710 --> 14:56.920
The Constitution
is in shreds.

14:56.920 --> 15:00.210
We, the people, have been
suffocated by their bare hands!

15:00.210 --> 15:01.880
This is
every man for himself,

15:01.880 --> 15:04.380
and I very much intend
to save myself.

15:04.380 --> 15:07.120
That is
my only concern!

15:09.830 --> 15:11.920
[ Door opens ]

15:17.580 --> 15:19.210
[ Sighs ]

15:26.880 --> 15:28.580
What did they do
to you?

15:32.620 --> 15:34.540
Leave.

15:35.830 --> 15:39.120
[ Inhales sharply ]

15:41.120 --> 15:43.250
[ Door opens ]

15:43.250 --> 15:51.170
♪♪

15:56.960 --> 15:58.580
The plan is to stay the course
while we figure out

15:58.580 --> 15:59.830
where these drones
are being controlled from

15:59.830 --> 16:01.210
and how
we defuse them.
"Stay the course"?

16:01.210 --> 16:02.500
So, do nothing?

16:02.500 --> 16:03.710
Not nothing.

16:03.710 --> 16:05.170
We're strategizing,
gathering information.

16:05.170 --> 16:06.830
Presenting a united front
to the press

16:06.830 --> 16:08.330
while
the President handles --
[ Door opens ]

16:08.330 --> 16:10.040
Mr. President.

16:10.040 --> 16:11.790
We were just updating
Mrs. Vargas on the situation.

16:11.790 --> 16:13.120
Thank you.

16:13.120 --> 16:14.420
Luna, could you
excuse us for a moment?

16:14.420 --> 16:15.380
Of course,
sir.

16:17.750 --> 16:19.170
Have the mayors
been briefed?

16:19.170 --> 16:20.960
All nine, sir.
I'd like them
followed up with.

16:20.960 --> 16:22.290
Every hour,
on the hour.

16:22.290 --> 16:24.540
Good.
What about FEMA?
FEMA?

16:24.540 --> 16:26.580
The Federal Emergency --
I know what FEMA is, sir.

16:26.580 --> 16:28.710
Then tell me you've
dispatched them to Philadelphia.

16:28.710 --> 16:31.000
I assumed you were speaking
with Director Morrison

16:31.000 --> 16:32.670
from the Sit Room,

16:32.670 --> 16:34.250
that the agency was following
your orders directly.

16:34.250 --> 16:36.420
You assumed?
That's all I can do,
sir,

16:36.420 --> 16:38.880
seeing how I haven't been
present in any of the meetings.

16:38.880 --> 16:40.040
It's fine.
I'll have someone else do it.

16:40.040 --> 16:41.670
No, sir,
I can do it.

16:41.670 --> 16:44.210
All remaining responders
will be sent to Philadelphia.

16:44.210 --> 16:45.710
They'll arrive
within the hour.

16:45.710 --> 16:48.210
We sure
we want to do that?

16:49.250 --> 16:50.580
What are you thinking?

16:50.580 --> 16:51.620
It's just...

16:51.620 --> 16:53.420
we send all
our federal responders

16:53.420 --> 16:54.920
to Dallas
and Philadelphia tonight,

16:54.920 --> 16:57.120
we'll be in big trouble if,
God forbid,

16:57.120 --> 16:59.120
those seven other whirligigs
go off.

16:59.120 --> 17:01.330
Might be better to ask
the governors to send in
local people for now,

17:01.330 --> 17:02.960
reassess the situation
in the morning.

17:05.290 --> 17:07.120
Fitz: Smart.

17:07.120 --> 17:09.330
Cyrus,
I want you with me.

17:09.330 --> 17:10.540
I have a briefing
I could use your help with.

17:10.540 --> 17:11.750
You got a tie?

17:11.750 --> 17:13.420
I think
I can find one, sir.
Let's go.

17:14.710 --> 17:16.580
[ Door closes ]

17:17.830 --> 17:20.880
[ Chatter ]

17:20.880 --> 17:23.170
Liv.
You got a second?

17:25.750 --> 17:27.040
So we've been
going through

17:27.040 --> 17:28.750
the files we pulled
from Peus' super PAC.

17:28.750 --> 17:31.120
Has your father ever mentioned
getting packages from them?

17:31.120 --> 17:33.500
Packages? No. Why?

17:33.500 --> 17:35.500
What is this?

17:35.500 --> 17:37.290
Invoices for a courier service
that made deliveries

17:37.290 --> 17:38.620
from the
Fund for American Renewal

17:38.620 --> 17:39.960
to your father's
work space,

17:39.960 --> 17:42.620
23 boxes in total,
each addressed to your father,

17:42.620 --> 17:44.330
each delivered separately
over several weeks.

17:44.330 --> 17:45.460
He never
mentioned them?

17:45.460 --> 17:47.120
No.

17:47.120 --> 17:50.330
Do you mind
if I keep these?
Sure.

17:50.330 --> 17:52.710
This Samantha woman --
she isn't talking?
No.
Let me amend that.

17:52.710 --> 17:54.710
She's talking a lot, she's just
not saying anything useful.

17:54.710 --> 17:56.080
Maybe it's time
to get creative.

17:56.080 --> 17:58.500
By "creative," you mean
what I think you mean, no.

17:58.500 --> 18:00.120
There are
seven more bombs, sir.

18:00.120 --> 18:02.920
Seven more cities
that could suffer losses.

18:02.920 --> 18:04.330
Yes, and if this were
Abu Ghraib,

18:04.330 --> 18:06.120
I'd say, by all means,
pull out her fingernails,

18:06.120 --> 18:07.500
but this is
the White House.

18:07.500 --> 18:08.880
She's on
White House grounds,

18:08.880 --> 18:10.170
and if we're going to
spit on the Constitution

18:10.170 --> 18:11.500
in the White House,

18:11.500 --> 18:13.290
we lose the right
to say we're better than them.

18:13.290 --> 18:14.920
I see
he hasn't changed.

18:14.920 --> 18:16.500
Fitz: What do we know
about this woman?

18:16.500 --> 18:18.750
Loves cats,
hates democracy.

18:18.750 --> 18:19.750
♪♪

18:19.750 --> 18:21.580
I'm only half-kidding.

18:21.580 --> 18:23.710
Does she have a TV?

18:23.710 --> 18:26.960
Anything in her cell?

18:26.960 --> 18:29.580
Wherever you're
keeping her, does she
have access to the news?

18:29.580 --> 18:31.620
No.
Why?

18:31.620 --> 18:33.540
Uh-huh. [ Chuckles ]

18:33.540 --> 18:35.080
This is perfect.

18:35.080 --> 18:37.500
Cyrus...
She knows nothing.

18:37.500 --> 18:39.670
In a cell,
your TV, your radio --

18:39.670 --> 18:40.880
it's your world.

18:40.880 --> 18:42.670
♪♪

18:42.670 --> 18:43.920
We can
tell her anything.

18:43.920 --> 18:45.290
♪♪

18:45.290 --> 18:47.040
She'll have no way
of confirming it.

18:47.040 --> 18:49.830
♪♪

18:49.830 --> 18:51.250
Come on.

18:51.250 --> 18:53.330
You can't be serious
with this crap.

18:53.330 --> 18:55.710
I'm serious.
We have Peus.

18:55.710 --> 18:57.880
No, you don't.
We do.

18:57.880 --> 19:00.210
Picked up his car on satellite,
sent a tail to track him,

19:00.210 --> 19:01.750
and followed him
to the drone control center.

19:01.750 --> 19:03.880
Our intent
was to follow him all the way,

19:03.880 --> 19:05.830
grab him, and neutralize
the drones all at once,

19:05.830 --> 19:07.620
but his driver realized
he was being tailed,

19:07.620 --> 19:09.670
so we had to move in
sooner than we wanted.

19:09.670 --> 19:12.000
I liked it better when
you were digging transmitters

19:12.000 --> 19:13.460
out of my neck
with a pen knife.

19:13.460 --> 19:15.670
That was fun.
This?

19:15.670 --> 19:17.460
Asking me to believe
this fish story?

19:17.460 --> 19:19.380
I honestly don't care
whether you believe me.

19:19.380 --> 19:21.580
I just came here to let you know
we're offering him immunity

19:21.580 --> 19:23.790
in exchange
for the control-center location.
Right.

19:23.790 --> 19:26.040
And let me guess, you're willing
to offer me the same

19:26.040 --> 19:27.420
if I talk
before he does.

19:27.420 --> 19:29.080
Nope.

19:29.080 --> 19:31.080
What do you mean,
"Nope"?

19:32.380 --> 19:34.710
Well,
I'll say it again slowly.

19:34.710 --> 19:35.880
We have Peus.

19:35.880 --> 19:38.000
I don't need you
at all.

19:38.000 --> 19:39.290
Okay.

19:39.290 --> 19:41.710
Then why
are you here?

19:41.710 --> 19:43.960
Mm. I'm here
because I asked to be.

19:43.960 --> 19:46.120
I'm here
because I don't like you.

19:46.120 --> 19:47.580
I'm here because I wanted
to be the one to tell you

19:47.580 --> 19:49.120
we took Peus

19:49.120 --> 19:51.210
and that you're never
going to see daylight again.

19:51.210 --> 19:55.170
I'm here to enjoy the
exact moment when it sinks in

19:55.170 --> 19:58.330
that you are completely
and royally screwed.

19:59.380 --> 20:01.880
[ Sighs ]

20:03.540 --> 20:04.750
Thank you.

20:04.750 --> 20:06.210
[ Chuckles ]

20:07.880 --> 20:11.830
Wait.
Just -- Just wait.

20:11.830 --> 20:14.120
You're better off
giving me the deal.

20:14.120 --> 20:15.580
Right.

20:15.580 --> 20:18.120
Wait!
Here's why.

20:18.120 --> 20:19.790
Offer it to Peus, all you're
getting is the drones.

20:19.790 --> 20:21.880
You're not getting names. You're
not getting bank accounts.

20:21.880 --> 20:23.830
Infrastructure.
I can get that for you.

20:23.830 --> 20:25.710
Give me his deal...

20:25.710 --> 20:27.580
I'll give you everything.

20:27.580 --> 20:29.880
♪♪

20:35.000 --> 20:36.170
How's it going out there?

20:36.170 --> 20:37.380
Do you still have
the surveillance video

20:37.380 --> 20:38.880
from my father's
dinosaur room?

20:38.880 --> 20:40.040
Yeah. Why?

20:40.040 --> 20:41.790
My father received
a package from Peus

20:41.790 --> 20:42.880
every two or three days

20:42.880 --> 20:44.210
starting the day
after the election.

20:44.210 --> 20:45.330
I want to know
what they were sending him.

20:45.330 --> 20:47.710
[ Sighs ]

20:52.120 --> 20:53.210
There.

21:00.210 --> 21:02.750
[ Keyboard clacks ]

21:02.750 --> 21:04.750
What's inside?

21:04.750 --> 21:06.710
I don't know.
I don't have a good angle on it.

21:06.710 --> 21:09.170
What did
he get on the 10th?

21:09.170 --> 21:10.500
[ Keyboard clacking ]

21:14.830 --> 21:17.750
♪♪

21:19.710 --> 21:21.790
I don't get it.
Is the box empty?

21:21.790 --> 21:23.380
Whatever it is,
it scares him.

21:36.500 --> 21:37.790
[ Keyboard clacking ]

21:41.830 --> 21:43.710
[ Keyboard clacks ]

21:43.710 --> 21:45.290
[ Keyboard clacks ]

21:50.460 --> 21:52.460
[ Keyboard clacking ]

21:55.710 --> 21:57.420
[ Keyboard clacks ]

22:03.080 --> 22:04.960
A brick?

22:04.960 --> 22:08.750
Why would
Peus send my father a brick?

22:08.750 --> 22:10.380
Let me see the invoices.

22:21.920 --> 22:24.120
It's for the weight.

22:24.120 --> 22:28.250
Every box weighed the same --
11 pounds.

22:28.250 --> 22:30.380
What does it mean?

22:30.380 --> 22:33.830
♪♪

22:33.830 --> 22:35.920
She's agreed to sign
the immunity deal -- Samantha.

22:35.920 --> 22:37.500
Yes, but she wants you
to deliver it.

22:37.500 --> 22:39.620
Okay.

22:39.620 --> 22:40.500
This is a good thing.

22:40.500 --> 22:42.040
Do I have to be nice to her?

22:42.040 --> 22:43.210
Be any way you want to be.

22:43.210 --> 22:44.670
Just keep your wits
about you.

22:44.670 --> 22:47.000
Do not get too close to her.
Do not let her touch you.

22:47.000 --> 22:48.170
Do you think
you can do that?

22:48.170 --> 22:49.710
Yeah.

22:51.830 --> 22:53.460
This is the deal?
That's the deal.

22:53.460 --> 22:54.960
You give us
everything you promised,

22:54.960 --> 22:56.380
we put an end
to all of this madness.

22:56.380 --> 22:58.710
I sign this immunity agreement,
you go free.

23:01.380 --> 23:02.920
Okay.
Please.

23:02.920 --> 23:04.880
Samantha, I'm afraid they're
gonna change their minds.

23:04.880 --> 23:06.620
[ Sighs ]

23:06.620 --> 23:07.880
Grace.

23:07.880 --> 23:09.290
I'm sorry?

23:09.290 --> 23:11.960
My name is Grace.
Grace Dennis.

23:11.960 --> 23:13.670
That's my name.
My real name.

23:13.670 --> 23:15.330
You actually have
a real name?

23:15.330 --> 23:17.290
I actually do.

23:17.290 --> 23:20.290
It says Samantha on the forms,
but I want this done right.

23:20.290 --> 23:21.750
I'll make sure
that's corrected.

23:25.210 --> 23:26.210
What?

23:26.210 --> 23:27.460
This is...

23:27.460 --> 23:28.790
[ Breathes deeply ]

23:28.790 --> 23:31.000
I don't know
how to say this.

23:31.000 --> 23:32.420
Um...

23:32.420 --> 23:34.330
can we start over?

23:34.330 --> 23:35.620
We don't have a lot of time.

23:35.620 --> 23:37.580
I'll make sure the changes
are implemented later.

23:37.580 --> 23:39.620
No.
You and me.

23:39.620 --> 23:41.540
You and me?

23:41.540 --> 23:44.000
You and me.
Let's start over.

23:44.000 --> 23:47.040
I mean, you know
my real name now.

23:47.040 --> 23:48.500
So it's a start.

23:48.500 --> 23:50.460
You murdered Elizabeth North.

23:50.460 --> 23:51.880
I know!

23:51.880 --> 23:53.620
I know I've done
terrible things, but --

23:53.620 --> 23:55.380
She was my friend,
and you murdered her.

23:55.380 --> 23:57.250
I was doing my job.

23:57.250 --> 23:59.420
Your job?
Your job?

24:01.290 --> 24:04.250
Listen to me
when I tell you this.

24:04.250 --> 24:05.460
I hate you.

24:05.460 --> 24:07.290
All of this,
this "you and me" --

24:07.290 --> 24:08.830
That was me doing my job.

24:08.830 --> 24:10.000
Everything
I've done with you,

24:10.000 --> 24:12.330
everything I've done to you,
has been...

24:12.330 --> 24:15.290
I've wanted to puke
every minute of every day,

24:15.290 --> 24:17.500
but I've persevered in
the interest of seeing you pay.

24:17.500 --> 24:19.000
You've been pretending?

24:19.000 --> 24:20.790
I've been pretending.

24:20.790 --> 24:21.960
You hate me?

24:21.960 --> 24:23.540
I hate you.

24:30.250 --> 24:32.290
Don't do that.
What are you doing?!

24:32.290 --> 24:34.080
I used to think
you were just twitchy.

24:34.080 --> 24:35.670
But I get it.
It's a tell.

24:35.670 --> 24:36.960
This is all a bluff.

24:36.960 --> 24:39.040
You don't have Peus.
You don't have anything.

24:39.040 --> 24:41.460
I -- You're wrong.

24:41.460 --> 24:43.790
Nope.
You twitch when you lie.

24:43.790 --> 24:45.330
But during that little speech
of yours,

24:45.330 --> 24:47.210
you didn't twitch at all,
because you meant that.

24:47.210 --> 24:49.960
You are actually
all hurt and upset

24:49.960 --> 24:51.580
about that disgusting woman.

24:51.580 --> 24:53.460
[ Grunts ]
[ Gasps ]

24:53.460 --> 24:55.380
[ Breathing heavily ]

25:01.670 --> 25:05.880
You better hope that I never get
out of here, David Rosen.

25:05.880 --> 25:08.620
I don't have to hope,
because you never will.

25:10.120 --> 25:12.120
Am I twitching now?

25:15.710 --> 25:17.710
[ Beep, door opens ]

25:20.250 --> 25:21.500
[ Door closes ]

25:21.500 --> 25:22.750
My father's
not working with them.

25:22.750 --> 25:24.830
How do you know?
They're sending him boxes.

25:24.830 --> 25:27.620
Every three days, a box with
a large brick inside shows up.

25:27.620 --> 25:29.880
A brick? Why?
I don't know.

25:29.880 --> 25:32.880
But each time one arrives,
he gets more and more agitated.

25:32.880 --> 25:34.960
They mean something to him,
something terrible.

25:34.960 --> 25:36.000
A box?

25:37.420 --> 25:39.540
With a brick in it?

25:39.540 --> 25:40.670
[ Breathes sharply ]

25:40.670 --> 25:42.750
I know it sounds crazy.

25:42.750 --> 25:44.540
But, somehow,
my father is being controlled

25:44.540 --> 25:46.380
for the first time
in his life.

25:46.380 --> 25:48.120
I need to talk to him again.

25:49.500 --> 25:51.080
Please.

25:57.880 --> 25:59.500
[ Door closes ]

26:02.000 --> 26:03.380
[ Sighs ]

26:19.670 --> 26:21.500
You think
about your legacy much?

26:23.170 --> 26:24.290
Worry about it?

26:28.500 --> 26:30.000
I do.

26:30.000 --> 26:31.830
I worry.

26:31.830 --> 26:33.290
Always have.

26:33.290 --> 26:37.750
And at times like these,
Americans are dying right now,

26:37.750 --> 26:39.330
and there's nothing
I can do about it.

26:39.330 --> 26:42.170
This will be my legacy.

26:42.170 --> 26:44.960
Eight years in office.

26:44.960 --> 26:49.080
All history will remember me
for is the body count.

26:49.080 --> 26:51.380
And your sex scandal.

26:53.920 --> 26:55.790
And that.

26:55.790 --> 26:58.120
I could have done better.

26:58.120 --> 27:00.120
I could have been better.

27:00.120 --> 27:02.420
I know that.
Well...

27:02.420 --> 27:04.000
good for you
for learning something.

27:04.000 --> 27:05.040
Are we done?

27:06.580 --> 27:08.460
Rowan, I know...

27:08.460 --> 27:10.250
about the boxes
they sent you.

27:12.460 --> 27:13.710
Do you?

27:13.710 --> 27:16.120
They sent you a box
every few days.

27:16.120 --> 27:18.620
Random days,
no pattern to it.

27:18.620 --> 27:21.250
Same weight every time.

27:21.250 --> 27:23.330
A brick inside every time.

27:23.330 --> 27:25.210
I know.

27:25.210 --> 27:26.880
You know nothing.

27:26.880 --> 27:29.290
You're as ignorant as a toddler
playing with a handgun,

27:29.290 --> 27:31.620
so you need
to cease speaking.

27:31.620 --> 27:33.210
I know
they were trying to scare you,

27:33.210 --> 27:34.580
trying to blackmail you,

27:34.580 --> 27:36.960
take your sense of control
away somehow.

27:38.750 --> 27:42.250
I have never been
in control of my own life.

27:42.250 --> 27:44.540
Hm.
Never at any step.

27:44.540 --> 27:48.210
I think I am,
but, really, I am surrounded

27:48.210 --> 27:50.580
by people who are experts
at pulling strings

27:50.580 --> 27:53.040
and making me think
I am in control.

27:53.040 --> 27:55.330
What I'm saying is that...

27:55.330 --> 27:58.000
you have taken so much
from me,

27:58.000 --> 27:59.580
and still...

28:01.500 --> 28:02.880
...I admire you.

28:02.880 --> 28:04.540
[ Scoffs ]

28:04.540 --> 28:06.790
You are not in control?

28:06.790 --> 28:09.040
That's what makes you
just like me?

28:09.040 --> 28:11.170
That's what makes you know?

28:11.170 --> 28:12.830
You never wanted control.

28:12.830 --> 28:14.460
You don't know
what control is.

28:14.460 --> 28:16.120
You are so...

28:18.750 --> 28:20.670
And she loves you.

28:20.670 --> 28:21.830
You!

28:21.830 --> 28:23.750
Let me explain something
to you.

28:23.750 --> 28:26.290
You will never
truly understand freedom

28:26.290 --> 28:28.040
because you've never been
in chains.

28:28.040 --> 28:31.750
No one has systematically
oppressed you, worn you down,

28:31.750 --> 28:37.330
kept your deepest fears
alive and well 24 hours a day!

28:37.330 --> 28:41.000
No one has ever broken you!!

28:47.960 --> 28:50.210
[ Sighs ]

28:50.210 --> 28:53.170
Random days.

28:53.170 --> 28:57.330
A box,
always 9 to 11 pounds.

28:57.330 --> 29:01.170
A brick inside every time.

29:01.170 --> 29:03.210
Sent just for me.

29:03.210 --> 29:04.830
And they were very clear.

29:04.830 --> 29:06.750
I should be grateful
to be serving them

29:06.750 --> 29:09.170
because the day I was
no longer helpful or cooperative

29:09.170 --> 29:10.380
was the day...

29:18.380 --> 29:22.420
The human head
weighs 9 to 11 pounds,

29:22.420 --> 29:23.830
the same
as one of those bricks.

29:23.830 --> 29:25.620
If I stopped cooperating,

29:25.620 --> 29:29.250
if they thought
I was not behaving...

29:29.250 --> 29:32.290
there would be a severed head
in that box.

29:34.750 --> 29:39.080
That head
would be Olivia's.

29:42.540 --> 29:44.500
You know nothing.

29:44.500 --> 29:48.170
And we are not alike
in any way.

29:48.170 --> 29:50.330
But you could take them down --

29:50.330 --> 29:52.170
now.

29:52.170 --> 29:53.460
This is your chance.

29:53.460 --> 29:56.080
You can't let them win.

29:56.080 --> 29:58.250
I joined the CIA
in the '70s.

29:58.250 --> 30:00.920
Nixon was out.
Conservatism was in.

30:00.920 --> 30:02.210
Look at me.

30:02.210 --> 30:04.960
I was a black man
with a short Afro.

30:04.960 --> 30:06.710
A perfect shot.

30:06.710 --> 30:09.120
I could code,
speak eight languages.

30:09.120 --> 30:12.460
Women loved me.
I was something.

30:12.460 --> 30:14.960
They were nervous about it.

30:14.960 --> 30:17.500
The halls of the U.S. government
shook at the thought

30:17.500 --> 30:19.210
of a black man
with that much power.

30:19.210 --> 30:21.250
No matter
what they did to stop me,

30:21.250 --> 30:24.710
I still climbed
all the way to the top.

30:24.710 --> 30:28.080
Nothing could stop my rise.

30:31.210 --> 30:33.580
That was then.

30:33.580 --> 30:35.380
Now?

30:35.380 --> 30:39.710
I'm a father incapable
of protecting my own daughter.

30:41.710 --> 30:43.170
No.

30:45.250 --> 30:47.920
Olivia is
what you're best at.

30:47.920 --> 30:50.290
That is what you do.

30:50.290 --> 30:52.750
You say
you protect the Republic,

30:52.750 --> 30:57.290
but, really,
she is your Republic.

30:59.170 --> 31:00.880
She is your legacy.

31:00.880 --> 31:03.750
How do you want history
to remember her?

31:07.920 --> 31:10.080
Thanks for the drink.

31:17.790 --> 31:21.210
[ Door opens, closes ]

31:28.620 --> 31:30.500
Evacuations are under way
in all the affected cities,

31:30.500 --> 31:31.790
and perimeters
are in place, sir.

31:31.790 --> 31:33.540
Good. Where are
my Predator drones, General?

31:33.540 --> 31:35.380
Armed and ready for launch.

31:35.380 --> 31:36.880
But there's been
a complication, sir.

31:36.880 --> 31:38.620
As the Philadelphia drone blew,

31:38.620 --> 31:40.580
the rest shifted
closer to nearby buildings,

31:40.580 --> 31:42.420
invalidating
our firing solution.

31:42.420 --> 31:45.000
If we hit the drones now,
without a clean firing solution,

31:45.000 --> 31:47.420
there's a chance the collateral
damage from our missiles

31:47.420 --> 31:49.540
will be worse
than the bombs themselves.

31:49.540 --> 31:50.710
We need more time,
Mr. President.

31:50.710 --> 31:51.920
We're out of time, General.

31:51.920 --> 31:53.330
Then we go now.

31:53.330 --> 31:56.420
Our pilots will do their best
to avoid collateral damage.

31:56.420 --> 31:57.880
It's your call, sir.

31:57.880 --> 31:59.500
[ Sighs ]

32:02.670 --> 32:04.290
No.

32:04.290 --> 32:06.210
They want us
to make a mistake.

32:06.210 --> 32:07.710
Let me know when it's safe
to take them out, General.

32:07.710 --> 32:08.750
Yes, sir.

32:12.750 --> 32:14.290
[ Camera shutter clicking ]

32:20.120 --> 32:22.330
Tell me
the latest number again.

32:22.330 --> 32:25.120
63.

32:25.120 --> 32:26.500
19 of them were children.

32:26.500 --> 32:28.120
Mm.

32:30.420 --> 32:33.500
Am I actually gonna bend
to a group of terrorists?

32:33.500 --> 32:35.380
No.
You're not.

32:35.380 --> 32:37.330
You can't.
I can. I did.

32:37.330 --> 32:40.380
I guess the real question is,
will I do it again?

32:41.830 --> 32:43.380
Fitz.

32:43.380 --> 32:45.460
I gave the terrorists
everything they asked for

32:45.460 --> 32:47.170
with West Angola, Liv.

32:48.620 --> 32:51.620
They had you.

32:51.620 --> 32:53.580
And I had no choice.

32:53.580 --> 32:56.120
You're not gonna make
that mistake again.

32:58.670 --> 33:00.250
She's the mother
of my children.

33:00.250 --> 33:02.710
Which is
exactly why you can't bend

33:02.710 --> 33:04.750
by handing her back to them.

33:06.790 --> 33:08.460
You think it's the booze

33:08.460 --> 33:10.960
that's making all of this
feel that much crazier?

33:10.960 --> 33:13.620
Should we stop drinking?

33:13.620 --> 33:18.880
All this would feel crazy
either way,

33:18.880 --> 33:21.380
so, no, we shouldn't.

33:21.380 --> 33:23.750
[ Chuckles ]

33:34.620 --> 33:37.670
This isn't the way I envisioned
our last two weeks together.

33:37.670 --> 33:39.040
Me neither.

33:41.290 --> 33:44.000
[ Knock on door, door opens ]

33:44.000 --> 33:45.920
Charlotte:
Mr. President.

33:45.920 --> 33:47.040
He'd like to see you.

33:47.040 --> 33:50.500
-I'm sorry to interrupt.
-Dad.

33:50.500 --> 33:53.710
Can I have a moment with
the president alone, sweetheart?

33:53.710 --> 33:55.880
[ Chuckles ]

34:01.210 --> 34:02.790
Of course.

34:14.540 --> 34:15.710
[ Door closes ]

34:15.710 --> 34:17.540
You came here
for another drink?

34:17.540 --> 34:21.290
I'm here...

34:21.290 --> 34:22.670
to apologize...

34:24.580 --> 34:26.670
...and to help.

34:26.670 --> 34:28.080
I think I know
how to make Samantha talk.

34:30.330 --> 34:32.620
I know
how difficult this must be.

34:32.620 --> 34:35.040
I want you to know
we will keep you safe.

34:35.040 --> 34:37.960
Fitz will keep you safe.

34:41.290 --> 34:44.790
[ Sighs ]

34:44.790 --> 34:46.380
Olivia, I'm sorry.

34:46.380 --> 34:49.000
You have nothing
to be sorry for.

34:49.000 --> 34:50.830
I'm afraid I do.

34:50.830 --> 34:52.670
-Hey, hey!
-Dad!

34:52.670 --> 34:54.710
Uncuff Ms. Wagner.

34:54.710 --> 34:56.750
Your prisoner --
Remove her cuffs! Now!

34:56.750 --> 34:58.210
Dad, what are you doing?

34:58.210 --> 35:01.210
What's going on, Eli?
What is this?

35:01.210 --> 35:03.380
I'm leaving the country.
I need my freedom.

35:03.380 --> 35:05.880
I need a guarantee
that I will be left alone,

35:05.880 --> 35:07.540
that your people
will leave me alone.

35:07.540 --> 35:09.880
If you can give me that, I will
take you with me -- right now.

35:09.880 --> 35:11.540
If not, you stay.

35:13.380 --> 35:14.960
The passcode for the tunnels --
What is it?

35:14.960 --> 35:16.580
There are no tunnels.

35:16.580 --> 35:18.420
[ Gunshot ]
Aah!

35:18.420 --> 35:20.170
Don't play me
for a fool, son.

35:20.170 --> 35:22.540
There's an exit to the tunnels
just down the hall.

35:22.540 --> 35:24.790
I need the passcode!

35:24.790 --> 35:26.790
7JL79.

35:26.790 --> 35:28.290
Now or never.

35:28.290 --> 35:30.290
Do you have the authority
to guarantee my freedom,

35:30.290 --> 35:31.380
or don't you?

35:34.830 --> 35:36.710
No. I don't.

35:36.710 --> 35:39.290
But you get me out of here,
and I'll get you that guarantee.

35:39.290 --> 35:41.250
Move.
Don't do this, Dad.
Please.

35:41.250 --> 35:42.500
I told you I was running.

35:42.500 --> 35:43.830
Dad! Dad!

35:43.830 --> 35:46.540
Dad!!

35:46.540 --> 35:47.710
This way.

35:47.710 --> 35:50.330
♪♪

35:55.830 --> 35:57.750
[ Indistinct conversations ]

35:57.750 --> 35:59.790
Cyrus.

35:59.790 --> 36:01.080
What's happening?
Why all the commotion?

36:01.080 --> 36:03.000
Not now, Red.
Is Fitz in there?

36:03.000 --> 36:04.500
What's he doing?
He's waiting for me.

36:04.500 --> 36:06.790
Please.
Cyrus, whatever's going on,

36:06.790 --> 36:08.170
let me in there with you.
I can help.

36:08.170 --> 36:10.670
Why should I let you in?
Because you asked nicely?

36:10.670 --> 36:12.420
You don't ask
to go to the Oval.

36:12.420 --> 36:14.330
Okay, I came clean.
I apologized.

36:14.330 --> 36:16.170
And now you're trying
to take my job.

36:16.170 --> 36:17.290
Haven't I been
punished enough?

36:17.290 --> 36:18.880
Nobody's punishing you, Red.

36:18.880 --> 36:20.830
You're punishing yourself.

36:20.830 --> 36:22.500
We're just doing our jobs.

36:22.500 --> 36:23.460
Nobody's trying
to take yours.

36:23.460 --> 36:24.960
You're giving it up.

36:24.960 --> 36:26.960
You want back in?
Don't ask.

36:26.960 --> 36:28.460
Prove that you deserve it.

36:28.460 --> 36:30.460
Get back in.

36:35.120 --> 36:36.040
[ Camera shutter clicking ]

36:41.330 --> 36:42.460
[ Door opens ]

36:42.460 --> 36:43.960
[ Sighs ]

36:46.040 --> 36:47.380
I heard about Rowan.

36:48.920 --> 36:51.120
Mellie,
I don't know what to say.

36:51.120 --> 36:53.920
They have killed
so many people.

36:53.920 --> 36:56.080
If this goes on any longer,
they will kill more.

36:56.080 --> 36:57.540
And the only reason
they are doing it

36:57.540 --> 36:59.920
is to get what they want,
which is me as their puppet.

36:59.920 --> 37:01.710
You are not going back
to them.

37:01.710 --> 37:04.830
I have already called a car
to the South Portico.

37:07.080 --> 37:08.420
It's over.

37:08.420 --> 37:09.420
It's not over.

37:09.420 --> 37:11.290
Olivia --
It's not over!

37:11.290 --> 37:14.620
You have never been and
never will be anyone's puppet.

37:14.620 --> 37:16.080
You are about to be

37:16.080 --> 37:18.460
the first female president
of the United States.

37:18.460 --> 37:20.830
Do you have any idea
how incredible that is?

37:20.830 --> 37:23.120
[ Sighs ]
How impossible?

37:23.120 --> 37:24.580
They almost handed this job

37:24.580 --> 37:27.960
to a man who had been in prison
over giving it to you.

37:27.960 --> 37:31.880
Why? Because a woman in power
is a nasty woman...

37:31.880 --> 37:34.420
a woman who needs
to be put in her place.

37:34.420 --> 37:37.330
That is what Peus and Samantha
want to do.

37:37.330 --> 37:40.170
They don't give a crap
about what you've sacrificed

37:40.170 --> 37:42.380
to get here --
every drop of blood,

37:42.380 --> 37:44.540
bead of sweat,
and falling tear.

37:44.540 --> 37:47.290
They just want to turn you
into a figurehead.

37:47.290 --> 37:48.750
And I will be damned

37:48.750 --> 37:51.920
if they turn the most
powerful person in the world

37:51.920 --> 37:56.250
into some princess whose only
power lies in a wave or a smile.

37:56.250 --> 37:58.580
This is
not their White House.

37:58.580 --> 38:00.040
It's ours.

38:00.040 --> 38:01.790
And neither one of us
is leaving without a fight.

38:01.790 --> 38:03.500
Trust.

38:03.500 --> 38:04.540
[ Door opens ]

38:08.790 --> 38:10.750
You done good, ole boy.

38:10.750 --> 38:12.250
I didn't do it
to earn your praise.

38:12.250 --> 38:14.420
I did it to be free --
from them, from you.

38:14.420 --> 38:16.580
So, we're clear.
The boxes stop.

38:16.580 --> 38:18.080
And when I'm gone,
I'm gone.

38:18.080 --> 38:20.330
And I never hear
from you again.

38:24.460 --> 38:26.960
I earned this!

38:26.960 --> 38:28.920
Agreed.

38:30.460 --> 38:31.880
Make the arrangements.

38:38.670 --> 38:40.420
[ Door opens, closes ]

38:42.460 --> 38:45.500
Congratulations, Eli.

38:45.500 --> 38:47.170
You've been emancipated.

38:52.040 --> 38:53.500
[ Door closes ]

38:54.330 --> 38:56.330
[ Dialing ]

38:56.330 --> 38:57.500
[ Door closes ]

38:57.500 --> 38:59.330
He's on the move.

38:59.330 --> 39:00.670
You here for another drink?

39:00.670 --> 39:02.790
I'm here to apologize...

39:04.290 --> 39:05.620
...and to help.

39:05.620 --> 39:07.250
I think I know
how to make Samantha talk.

39:07.250 --> 39:08.750
You think you can break her?

39:08.750 --> 39:10.920
I'll do better.
I'll gain her trust.

39:10.920 --> 39:12.290
[ Camera shutter clicks ]
Dad!

39:12.290 --> 39:14.040
Uncuff Ms. Wagner.

39:14.040 --> 39:16.080
Your prisoner --
Remove her cuffs! Now!

39:16.080 --> 39:17.880
Dad, what are you doing?

39:17.880 --> 39:19.750
I'll force
a meeting with Peus,

39:19.750 --> 39:21.000
let him lead us
to the drones.

39:21.000 --> 39:23.500
Congratulations, Eli.

39:23.500 --> 39:24.960
You've been emancipated.

39:26.790 --> 39:28.540
He's on the move.

39:28.540 --> 39:29.620
That's where you come in.

39:29.620 --> 39:31.670
Roger that.

39:31.670 --> 39:33.250
[ Camera shutter clicks ]

39:33.250 --> 39:34.750
Who's next -- Miami?

39:34.750 --> 39:35.710
[ Silenced gunshots ]

39:37.500 --> 39:39.290
You.

39:39.290 --> 39:40.580
You're next.

39:45.080 --> 39:47.710
And once
Jake's taken care of Peus,

39:47.710 --> 39:48.960
what happens
to Samantha Wagner?

39:51.210 --> 39:52.460
[ Camera shutter clicks ]

39:52.460 --> 39:54.790
Cash, passport, condoms --

39:54.790 --> 39:56.750
everything you'll need
for Zanzibar or wherever.

39:56.750 --> 39:57.960
Mm.

39:57.960 --> 39:59.500
What's in the box?

39:59.500 --> 40:01.460
A tooth, for her.

40:01.460 --> 40:03.000
The last piece
of the puzzle.

40:03.000 --> 40:04.710
It must have come
while we were detained.

40:04.710 --> 40:06.250
Well, here.
Have a look.

40:08.580 --> 40:10.290
It's empty.
Mm-hmm.

40:10.290 --> 40:11.540
Aah! [ Gasps ]

40:11.540 --> 40:14.670
This is freedom.

40:14.670 --> 40:16.540
[ Gasping ]

40:19.290 --> 40:22.710
As abruptly as it began,
the crisis has come to an end.

40:22.710 --> 40:25.170
According to reports
from the cities under siege,

40:25.170 --> 40:27.670
all remaining drones
have been neutralized.

40:27.670 --> 40:30.580
Evacuation orders have been
lifted in those cities,

40:30.580 --> 40:31.960
while emergency relief efforts

40:31.960 --> 40:34.710
continue
in Philadelphia and Dallas.

40:34.710 --> 40:37.500
While the origin of the drones
remains a mystery...
It's over.

40:37.500 --> 40:40.290
...the president is expected
to address the nation shortly.

40:40.290 --> 40:43.290
For now, however, the worst
seems to be behind us.

40:43.290 --> 40:46.330
While the rubble is cleared
in Philadelphia and Dallas,

40:46.330 --> 40:49.120
residents in those two cities
say they have been overwhelmed

40:49.120 --> 40:51.540
by the support
of their fellow Americans.

40:51.540 --> 40:54.000
Vigils are planned across
the country tomorrow night

40:54.000 --> 40:55.750
to mourn
the victims of the attacks,

40:55.750 --> 40:58.620
but also to celebrate the
heroes who opened their homes,

40:58.620 --> 41:00.330
contributed
to the relief efforts,

41:00.330 --> 41:02.790
and provided valuable intel
to the White House.

41:02.790 --> 41:04.790
Mayors Silachi and Barta

41:04.790 --> 41:06.540
will meet in Washington
Wednesday night

41:06.540 --> 41:08.960
to honor
several of those men and women.

41:11.460 --> 41:12.960
That's it.

41:15.880 --> 41:17.000
There you are.

41:17.000 --> 41:18.620
[ Laughs ]

41:22.830 --> 41:24.210
You made it.

41:24.210 --> 41:25.670
You survived.

41:28.210 --> 41:30.000
[ Camera shutter clicking ]

41:34.750 --> 41:38.120
♪♪
